relay_log_purge
Disables or enables automatic purging of relay log files as           soon as they are not needed any more. The default value is 1           (ON).  Disable or enable automatic purging of relay logs as soon as           they are no longer needed. The default value is 1 (enabled).           This is a global variable that can be changed dynamically with           SET GLOBAL relay_log_purge =           N. 